  "detailed_description": "<strong>TRIOS </strong>is a game about numbers and the fun you can have with them. Deceptively simple, surprisingly challenging. <br><br>Select two numbers and one operator, then watch them combine to create a new number. Use all your numbers to reach the target. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1214060/extras/53d45cd4902eb73ec67e396137a18d84.poster.avif?t=1758511451\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1214060/extras/53d45cd4902eb73ec67e396137a18d84.webm?t=1758511451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1214060/extras/53d45cd4902eb73ec67e396137a18d84.mp4?t=1758511451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Journey mode: A series of puzzles with escalating difficulty<br></li><li>Infinite mode: Randomly generated puzzles that adapt difficulty to your pace<br></li><li>A selection of chill tunes and beautiful backgrounds to guide you into flow</li></ul>",
